H0.text: What tiny peoples tied up Gulliver while he was asleep. Lilliputians

H1.text: What tiny peoples tied up Gulliver while he was asleep. Munchkins

H2.text: What tiny peoples tied up Gulliver while he was asleep. Smurfs

H3.text: What tiny peoples tied up Gulliver while he was asleep. Blefuscu

A4.text: Gulliver washes up on the shore of Lilliput and is captured by the inhabitants while asleep.

A5.text: Gulliver is, after further adventures, condemned as a traitor by the Council of Lilliput, and condemned to be blinded; he escapes his punishment by fleeing to Blefuscu.
